<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>197</hymn_number>
<author>C.Z. Huala</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuhin buoina tangsip a ding in,
 Ngaklah in khaw thiengtho ka thil;
 Tu chana ka ngilhloh lungtuok te,
 Puonvam silh a a lennau,

[V2]
 Ei haw ki'n la, ka hun ngak hi,
 Ka kahna gam za mah lele;
 Tatsate tuol nuom a lennau chu,
 Mun galmuong chu ei tunin.

[V3]
 2. Aw kei di'n khawvel hi hak mahleh,
 Kumsawt taikhuo a hung vak tieng,
 &quot;Buoina cheng hi bei ding&quot; a tiu ie,
 Ka ngaklah ni lopi chu,

[V4]
 3. A sawt taluoi kei dingin buoina,
 Pak bang tuoi hen lei dahum hi;
 Muh ka nuom hi tatte tuol lenna,
 Lungdeih peh bang kim tanau,

[V5]
 4. Damlai gamgaw hi ka pelh tieng leh,
 Van mithiengte laituol lenna,
 Kikhen loin chawlhna thing limah,
 Hailo in la sak pih ka.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Ngaklah Ni Lopi Chu</title>
</song>